S. African Union Declares Dispute With Xstrata Over Share Plan

-- B y   R o b e r t   B r a n d
-- 
2011-08-21T12:16:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/s-african-union-declares-dispute-with-xstrata-over-share-plan.html
South Africa ’s National Union of
Mineworkers sys it’s in dispute with  Xstrata Plc (XTA)  over a share
ownership plan for employees, union spokesman Lesiba Seshoka
said.  The union opposes the company’s decision to award shares to
workers according to their job grade instead of distributing
them equally, Seshoka said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
